headline: Eastman Schedules First-Quarter 2025 Financial Results News Release and SEC Form 8-K Filing, Teleconference and Webcast, and Release of Additional Information
summary: KINGSPORT, Tenn., April 11, 2025--Eastman has scheduled its first-quarter 2025 financial results news release and SEC Form 8-K filing, teleconference and webcast.
